12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">n) </span><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\">(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</a></span></em></p>'),(128,56,NULL,205,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">o) </span><em><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\">(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</a></span></em></p>'),(129,56,NULL,205,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">p) <em><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2015/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-12-29-outubro-2015-781847-publicacaooriginal-148557-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea acrescida pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 12, de 2015,</a> </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">e</span><span style=\"color: red;\"> </span></em></span><em><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\">revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</a></span></em></p>'),(130,56,NULL,206,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">a) assuntos atinentes a urbanismo e arquitetura; pol&iacute;tica e desenvolvimento urbano; uso, parcelamento e ocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o do solo urbano; habita&ccedil;&atilde;o e sistema financeiro da habita&ccedil;&atilde;o; transportes urbanos; infra-estrutura urbana e saneamento ambiental;</span></p>'),(131,56,NULL,206,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">b) mat&eacute;rias relativas a direito urban&iacute;stico e a ordena&ccedil;&atilde;o jur&iacute;dico-urban&iacute;stica do territ&oacute;rio; planos nacionais e regionais de ordena&ccedil;&atilde;o do territ&oacute;rio e da organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o pol&iacute;tico-administrativa;</span></p>'),(132,56,NULL,206,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">c) pol&iacute;tica e desenvolvimento municipal e territorial;</span></p>'),(133,56,NULL,206,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 2cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">d) mat&eacute;rias referentes ao direito municipal e ed&iacute;lico;</span></p>'),(134,56,NULL,206,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 2cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">e) regi&otilde;es metropolitanas, aglomera&ccedil;&otilde;es urbanas, regi&otilde;es integradas de desenvolvimento e microrregi&otilde;es;</span></p>'),(135,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">a) recebimento, avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o e investiga&ccedil;&atilde;o de den&uacute;ncias relativas a amea&ccedil;a ou viola&ccedil;&atilde;o de direitos humanos;</span></p>'),(136,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">b) fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e acompanhamento de programas governamentais relativos &agrave; prote&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos humanos;</span></p>'),(137,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">c) colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o com entidades n&atilde;o-governamentais, nacionais e internacionais, que atuem na defesa dos direitos humanos;</span></p>'),(138,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">d) pesquisas e estudos relativos &agrave; situa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos humanos no Brasil e no mundo, inclusive para efeito de divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica e fornecimento de subs&iacute;dios para as demais Comiss&otilde;es da Casa;</span></p>'),(139,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">e) assuntos referentes &agrave;s minorias; </span><em><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</a></span></em></p>'),(140,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">f) preserva&ccedil;&atilde;o e prote&ccedil;&atilde;o das culturas populares e &eacute;tnicas do Pa&iacute;s;</span></p>'),(141,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">g) promo&ccedil;&atilde;o da igualdade racial; <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2016/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-15-28-abril-2016-782949-publicacaooriginal-150191-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea acrescida pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 15, de 2016)</a></em></span></p>'),(142,56,NULL,207,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">h) assuntos referentes aos povos quilombolas; </span><em><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"><a href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea acrescida pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</a></span></em></p>'),(143,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">a) assuntos atinentes &agrave; educa&ccedil;&atilde;o em geral; <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(144,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">b) pol&iacute;tica e sistema educacional, em seus aspectos institucionais, estruturais, funcionais e legais; <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(145,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">c) direito da educa&ccedil;&atilde;o; <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(146,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">d) recursos humanos e financeiros para a educa&ccedil;&atilde;o; <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(147,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">e) <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(148,56,NULL,208,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt;\">f) <em><a href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-27-fevereiro-2013-775437-publicacaooriginal-139135-pl.html\">(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n<span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&ordm;</span> 21, de 2013)</a></em></span></p>'),(149,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) sistema financeiro nacional e entidades a ele vinculadas; mercado financeiro e de capitais; autoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o para funcionamento das institui&ccedil;&otilde;es financeiras; opera&ccedil;&otilde;es financeiras; cr&eacute;dito; bolsas de valores e de mercadorias; sistema de poupan&ccedil;a; capta&ccedil;&atilde;o e garantia da poupan&ccedil;a popular;</span></p>'),(150,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) sistema financeiro da habita&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(151,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) sistema nacional de seguros privados e capitaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(152,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) t&iacute;tulos e valores mobili&aacute;rios;</span></p>'),(153,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) regime jur&iacute;dico do capital estrangeiro; remessa de lucros;</span></p>'),(154,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">f) d&iacute;vida p&uacute;blica interna e externa;</span></p>'),(155,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">g) mat&eacute;rias financeiras e or&ccedil;ament&aacute;rias p&uacute;blicas, ressalvada a compet&ecirc;ncia da Comiss&atilde;o Mista Permanente a que se refere o art. 166, &sect; 1&ordm;, da Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal; normas gerais de direito financeiro; normas gerais de licita&ccedil;&atilde;o e contrata&ccedil;&atilde;o, em todas as modalidades, para a administra&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica direta e indireta, inclu&iacute;das as funda&ccedil;&otilde;es institu&iacute;das e mantidas pelo Poder P&uacute;blico;</span></p>'),(156,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">h) aspectos financeiros e or&ccedil;ament&aacute;rios p&uacute;blicos de quaisquer proposi&ccedil;&otilde;es que importem aumento ou diminui&ccedil;&atilde;o da receita ou da despesa p&uacute;blica, quanto &agrave; sua compatibilidade ou adequa&ccedil;&atilde;o com o plano plurianual, a lei de diretrizes or&ccedil;ament&aacute;rias e o or&ccedil;amento anual;</span></p>'),(157,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">i) fixa&ccedil;&atilde;o da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o dos membros do Congresso Nacional, do Presidente e do Vice-Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica, dos Ministros de Estado e dos membros da magistratura federal;</span></p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>'),(158,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">j) sistema tribut&aacute;rio nacional e reparti&ccedil;&atilde;o das receitas tribut&aacute;rias; normas gerais de direito tribut&aacute;rio; legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o referente a cada tributo;</span></p>'),(159,56,NULL,209,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">l) tributa&ccedil;&atilde;o, arrecada&ccedil;&atilde;o, fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o; parafiscalidade; empr&eacute;stimos compuls&oacute;rios; contribui&ccedil;&otilde;es sociais; administra&ccedil;&atilde;o fiscal;</span></p>'),(160,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) tomada de contas do Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica, na hip&oacute;tese do art. 51, II, da Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal;</span></p>'),(161,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) acompanhamento e fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o cont&aacute;bil, financeira, or&ccedil;ament&aacute;ria, operacional e patrimonial da Uni&atilde;o e das entidades da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o direta e indireta, inclu&iacute;das as sociedades e funda&ccedil;&otilde;es institu&iacute;das e mantidas pelo Poder P&uacute;blico federal, sem preju&iacute;zo do exame por parte das demais Comiss&otilde;es nas &aacute;reas das respectivas compet&ecirc;ncias e em articula&ccedil;&atilde;o com a Comiss&atilde;o Mista Permanente de que trata o art. 166, &sect; 1&ordm;, da Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal;</span></p>'),(162,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) planos e programas de desenvolvimento nacional ou regional, ap&oacute;s exame, pelas demais Comiss&otilde;es, dos programas que lhes disserem respeito;</span></p>'),(163,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) representa&ccedil;&otilde;es do Tribunal de Contas solicitando susta&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato impugnado ou outras provid&ecirc;ncias a cargo do Congresso Nacional, elaborando, em caso de parecer favor&aacute;vel, o respectivo projeto de decreto legislativo (Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal, art. 71, &sect; 1&ordm;);</span></p>'),(164,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) exame dos relat&oacute;rios de atividades do Tribunal de Contas da Uni&atilde;o (Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal, art. 71, &sect; 4&ordm;);</span></p>'),(165,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">f) requisi&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, relat&oacute;rios, balan&ccedil;os e inspe&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre as contas ou autoriza&ccedil;&otilde;es de despesas de &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o federal, diretamente ou por interm&eacute;dio do Tribunal de Contas da Uni&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(166,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2cm; font-size: 12pt;\">g) implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o do Plano Anual de Fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e Controle (PAFC), nos termos do art. 61-A deste Regimento; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-indent: 2cm; color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2017/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-25-7-dezembro-2017-785900-publicacaooriginal-154456-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Al&iacute;nea acrescida pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n</em></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-indent: 2cm; color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2017/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-25-7-dezembro-2017-785900-publicacaooriginal-154456-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>&ordm;</em></span></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-indent: 2cm; color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2017/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-25-7-dezembro-2017-785900-publicacaooriginal-154456-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> 25, de 2017)</em></span></a></u></span>f) requisi&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, relat&oacute;rios, balan&ccedil;os e inspe&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre as contas ou autoriza&ccedil;&otilde;es de despesas de &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o federal, diretamente ou por interm&eacute;dio do Tribunal de Contas da Uni&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(167,56,NULL,210,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">h) apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o do Relat&oacute;rio Anual de Fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e Controle (RAFC), nos termos do &sect; 1&ordm; do art. 61-A deste Regimento. </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2