 oriundas de entidades cient&iacute;ficas e culturais e de qualquer das entidades mencionadas na al&iacute;nea </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>a</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> deste inciso;</span></span></p>'),(170,56,NULL,212,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) pol&iacute;tica e sistema nacional do meio ambiente; direito ambiental; legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o de defesa ecol&oacute;gica;</span></p>'),(171,56,NULL,212,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) recursos naturais renov&aacute;veis; flora, fauna e solo; edafologia e desertifica&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(172,56,NULL,212,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) desenvolvimento sustent&aacute;vel;</span></p>'),(173,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) pol&iacute;ticas e modelos mineral e energ&eacute;tico brasileiros;</span></p>'),(174,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) a estrutura institucional e o papel dos agentes dos setores mineral e energ&eacute;tico;</span></p>'),(175,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) fontes convencionais e alternativas de energia;</span></p>'),(176,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) pesquisa e explora&ccedil;&atilde;o de recursos minerais e energ&eacute;ticos;</span></p>'),(177,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) formas de acesso ao bem mineral; empresas de minera&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(179,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">f) pol&iacute;tica e estrutura de pre&ccedil;os de recursos energ&eacute;ticos;</span></p>'),(180,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">g) comercializa&ccedil;&atilde;o e industrializa&ccedil;&atilde;o de min&eacute;rios;</span></p>'),(181,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">h) fomento &agrave; atividade mineral;</span></p>'),(182,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">i) regime jur&iacute;dico dos bens minerais e dos recursos energ&eacute;ticos;</span></p>'),(183,56,NULL,213,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">j) gest&atilde;o, planejamento e controle dos recursos h&iacute;dricos; regime jur&iacute;dico de &aacute;guas p&uacute;blicas e particulares;</span></p>'),(184,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) rela&ccedil;&otilde;es diplom&aacute;ticas e consulares, econ&ocirc;micas e comerciais, culturais e cient&iacute;ficas com outros pa&iacute;ses; rela&ccedil;&otilde;es com entidades internacionais multilaterais e regionais;</span></p>'),(185,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) pol&iacute;tica externa brasileira; servi&ccedil;o exterior brasileiro;</span></p>'),(186,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) tratados, atos, acordos e conv&ecirc;nios internacionais e demais instrumentos de pol&iacute;tica externa;</span></p>'),(187,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) direito internacional p&uacute;blico; ordem jur&iacute;dica internacional; nacionalidade; cidadania e naturaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o; regime jur&iacute;dico dos estrangeiros; emigra&ccedil;&atilde;o e imigra&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(188,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) autoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o para o Presidente ou o Vice-Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica ausentar-se do territ&oacute;rio nacional;</span></p>'),(189,56,NULL,214,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',