ckground-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o com entidades n&atilde;o governamentais, nacionais e internacionais, que atuem na defesa dos direitos das pessoas com defici&ecirc;ncia;</span></p>'),(269,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) recebimento, avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o e investiga&ccedil;&atilde;o de den&uacute;ncias relativas &agrave; amea&ccedil;a ou &agrave; viola&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos da mulher, em especial as v&iacute;timas de viol&ecirc;ncia dom&eacute;stica, f&iacute;sica, psicol&oacute;gica e moral, e respectiva discuss&atilde;o e delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(270,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e acompanhamento de programas governamentais relativos &agrave; prote&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos da mulher, visando ao seu empoderamento na sociedade brasileira;</span></p>'),(271,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\">c) incentivo e fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de programas de apoio &agrave;s mulheres chefes de fam&iacute;lia monoparentais;</span>b) fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e acompanhamento de programas governamentais relativos &agrave; prote&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos da mulher, visando ao seu empoderamento na sociedade brasileira;</span></p>'),(272,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) monitoramento da sa&uacute;de materno-infantil e neonatal, dos programas de apoio a mulheres em estado puerperal, em especial nas regi&otilde;es mais carentes do Pa&iacute;s;</span></p>'),(274,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) incentivo e monitoramento dos programas de preven&ccedil;&atilde;o e de enfrentamento do c&acirc;ncer do &uacute;tero, do colo do &uacute;tero, do ov&aacute;rio e de mama;</span></p>'),(275,56,NULL,222,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initia