te;blicos;</span></p>'),(323,56,NULL,228,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">f) presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os p&uacute;blicos em geral e seu regime jur&iacute;dico. </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2023/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-1-8-fevereiro-2023-793775-publicacaooriginal-167068-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Inciso acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2023)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(324,74,NULL,277,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) sinopse da correspond&ecirc;ncia e outros documentos recebidos e da agenda da Comiss&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(325,74,NULL,277,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) comunica&ccedil;&atilde;o das mat&eacute;rias distribu&iacute;das aos Relatores; </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/1994/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-58-24-fevereiro-1994-321558-norma-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">(</span></a></u></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/1994/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-58-24-fevereiro-1994-321558-norma-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>Al&iacute;nea adaptada aos termos da Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 58, de 1994,</em></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/int/atomes/2005/atodamesa-71-14-dezembro-2005-540316-publicacaooriginal-40423-cd-mesa.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>conforme republica&ccedil;&atilde;o determinada pelo Ato da Mesa n&ordm; 71, de 2005)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(326,74,NULL,278,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) conhecimento, exame ou instru&ccedil;&atilde;o de mat&eacute;ria de natureza legislativa, fiscalizat&oacute;ria ou informativa, ou outros assuntos da al&ccedil;ada da Comiss&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(327,74,NULL,278,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) discuss&atilde;o e vota&ccedil;&atilde;o de requerimentos e relat&oacute;rios em geral:</span></p>'),(328,74,NULL,278,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) discuss&atilde;o e vota&ccedil;&atilde;o de proposi&ccedil;&otilde;es e respectivos pareceres sujeitos &agrave; aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o do Plen&aacute;rio da C&acirc;mara;</span></p>'),(329,74,NULL,278,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) discuss&atilde;o e vota&ccedil;&atilde;o de projetos de lei e respectivos pareceres que dispensarem a aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o do Plen&aacute;rio da C&acirc;mara.</span></p>'),(330,81,NULL,304,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) favor&aacute;veis - os \"pelas conclus&otilde;es&rsquo;, \"com restri&ccedil;&otilde;es\" e \"em separado\" n&atilde;o divergentes das conclus&otilde;es;</span></p>'),(331,81,NULL,304,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) contr&aacute;rios - os \"vencidos\" e os \"em separado\" divergentes das conclus&otilde;es;</span></p>'),(332,81,NULL,310,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) frustrada a reclama&ccedil;&atilde;o escrita do Presidente da Comiss&atilde;o, o fato ser&aacute; comunicado &agrave; Mesa;</span></p>'),(333,81,NULL,310,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) o Presidente da C&acirc;mara far&aacute; apelo a este membro da Comiss&atilde;o no sentido de atender &agrave; reclama&ccedil;&atilde;o, fixando-lhe para isso o prazo de duas sess&otilde;es;</span></p>'),(334,81,NULL,310,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) se, vencido o prazo, n&atilde;o houver sido atendido o apelo, o Presidente da C&acirc;mara designar&aacute; substituto na Comiss&atilde;o para o membro faltoso, por indica&ccedil;&atilde;o do L&iacute;der da bancada respectiva, e mandar&aacute; proceder &agrave; restaura&ccedil;&atilde;o dos autos;</span></p>'),(335,90,NULL,357,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) ordin&aacute;rias, as de qualquer sess&atilde;o legislativa, realizadas apenas uma vez por dia, de ter&ccedil;a a quinta-feira, iniciando-se &agrave;s quatorze horas;</span></p>'),(336,90,NULL,357,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) extraordin&aacute;rias, as realizadas em dias ou horas diversos dos prefixados para as ordin&aacute;rias; </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2012/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-19-17-outubro-2012-774411-norma-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Inciso com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 19, de 2012)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(337,90,NULL,358,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) de debates, as realizadas de forma id&ecirc;ntica &agrave;s ordin&aacute;rias, por&eacute;m com dura&ccedil;&atilde;o de cinco horas e sem Ordem do Dia, apenas uma vez &agrave;s segundas e sextas-feiras, iniciando-se &agrave;s quatorze horas nas segundas-feiras e &agrave;s nove horas nas sextas-feiras, podendo os L&iacute;deres delegar a membros de suas bancadas o tempo relativo &agrave;s Comunica&ccedil;&otilde;es de Lideran&ccedil;as; </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2021/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-12-maio-2021-791358-publicacaooriginal-162824-cd-presi.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 21, de 2021)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(338,90,NULL,358,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) solenes, as realizadas para grandes comemora&ccedil;&otilde;es ou homenagens especiais, por prazo n&atilde;o excedente a quatro horas. </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2021/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-21-12-maio-2021-791358-publicacaooriginal-162824-cd-presi.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Al&iacute;nea com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 21, de 2021)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(339,110,227,402,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) prefer&ecirc;ncia;</span></p>'),(340,110,227,402,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) adiamento;</span></p>'),(341,110,227,402,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) retirada da Ordem do Dia;</span></p>'),(342,110,227,402,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) invers&atilde;o de pauta.</span></p>'),(343,128,NULL,417,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; back