f; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/int/rescad/2022/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-33-4-agosto-2022-793091-publicacaooriginal-165882-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 33, de 2022)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(374,171,NULL,527,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/int/rescad/2022/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-33-4-agosto-2022-793091-publicacaooriginal-165882-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Revogada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 33, de 2022)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(375,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) sobre declara&ccedil;&atilde;o de guerra, celebra&ccedil;&atilde;o de paz, ou remessa de for&ccedil;as brasileiras para o exterior;</span></p>'),(376,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) sobre suspens&atilde;o das imunidades de Deputados, na vig&ecirc;ncia do estado de sitio ou de sua prorroga&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(377,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) sobre requisi&ccedil;&atilde;o de civis e militares em tempo de guerra, ou quaisquer provid&ecirc;ncias que interessem &agrave; defesa e &agrave; seguran&ccedil;a do Pa&iacute;s;</span></p>'),(378,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) sobre decreta&ccedil;&atilde;o de impostos, na imin&ecirc;ncia ou em caso de guerra externa;</span></p>'),(379,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">e) sobre medidas financeiras ou legais, em caso de guerra;</span></p>'),(380,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">f) sobre transfer&ecirc;ncia tempor&aacute;ria da sede do Governo Federal;</span></p>'),(381,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">g) sobre permiss&atilde;o para que for&ccedil;as estrangeiras transitem pelo territ&oacute;rio nacional ou nele permane&ccedil;am temporariamente;</span></p>'),(382,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">h) sobre interven&ccedil;&atilde;o federal, ou modifica&ccedil;&atilde;o das condi&ccedil;&otilde;es de interven&ccedil;&atilde;o em vigor;</span></p>'),(383,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">i) sobre autoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o ao Presidente ou ao Vice-Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica para se ausentarem do Pais;</span></p>'),(384,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">j) oriundas de mensagens do Poder Executivo que versem sobre acordos, tratados, conven&ccedil;&otilde;es, pactos, conv&ecirc;nios, protocolos e demais instrumentos de pol&iacute;tica internacional, a partir de sua aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o pelo &oacute;rg&atilde;o t&eacute;cnico espec&iacute;fico, atrav&eacute;s de projeto de decreto legislativo, ou que sejam por outra forma apreciadas conclusivamente;</span></p>'),(385,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">j) oriundas de mensagens do Poder Executivo que versem sobre acordos, tratados, conven&ccedil;&otilde;es, pactos, conv&ecirc;nios, protocolos e demais instrumentos de pol&iacute;tica internacional, a partir de sua aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o pelo &oacute;rg&atilde;o t&eacute;cnico espec&iacute;fico, atrav&eacute;s de projeto de decreto legislativo, ou que sejam por outra forma apreciadas conclusivamente;</span></p>'),(386,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">l) de iniciativa do Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica, com solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o de urg&ecirc;ncia;</span></p>'),(387,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">m) constitu&iacute;das pelas emendas do Senado Federal a projetos referidos na al&iacute;nea anterior;</span></p>'),(388,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">n) referidas no art. 15, XII;</span></p>'),(389,179,NULL,535,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">o) reconhecidas, por delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o do Plen&aacute;rio, de car&aacute;ter urgente, nas hip&oacute;teses do art. 153;</span></p>'),(390,179,NULL,536,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) os projetos de iniciativa do Poder Executivo, do Poder Judici&aacute;rio, do Minist&eacute;rio P&uacute;blico, da Mesa, de Comiss&atilde;o Permanente ou Especial, do Senado Federal ou dos cidad&atilde;os;</span></p>'),(391,179,NULL,536,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) os projetos:</span></p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1 - de leis complementares e ordin&aacute;rias que se destinem a regulamentar dispositivo constitucional, e suas altera&ccedil;&otilde;es;</span></p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2 - de lei com prazo determinado;</span></p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3 - de regulamenta&ccedil;&atilde;o de elei&ccedil;&otilde;es, e suas altera&ccedil;&otilde;es;</span></p>\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4 - de altera&ccedil;&atilde;o ou reforma do Regimento Interno;</span></p>'),(392,220,NULL,684,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) se for supressiva;</span></p>'),(393,220,NULL,684,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) se for substitutiva de artigo da emenda, e a vota&ccedil;&atilde;o desta se fizer artigo por artigo;</span></p>'),(394,261,569,724,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) firmar ou manter contrato com pessoa jur&iacute;dica de direito p&uacute;blico, autarquia, empresa p&uacute;blica, sociedade de economia mista ou empresa concession&aacute;ria de servi&ccedil;o p&uacute;blico, salvo quando o contrato obedecer a cl&aacute;usulas uniformes;</span></p>'),(395,261,569,724,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) aceitar ou exercer cargo, fun&ccedil;&atilde;o ou emprego remunerado, inclusive os de que sejam demiss&iacute;veis </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>ad nutum</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">, nas entidades constantes da al&iacute;nea anterior;</span></span></p>'),(396,261,569,725,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) ser propriet&aacute;rios, controladores ou diretores de empresa que goze de favor decorrente de contrato com pessoa jur&iacute;dica de direito p&uacute;blico, ou nela exercer fun&ccedil;&atilde;o remunerada;</span></p>'),(397,261,569,725,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) ocupar cargo ou fun&ccedil;&atilde;o de que sejam demiss&iacute;veis </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>ad nutum</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">, nas entidades referidas no inciso I, </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>a</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">;</span></span></p>'),(398,261,569,725,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">c) patrocinar causa em que seja interessada qualquer das entidades a que se refere o inciso I, </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>a</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">;</span></span></p>'),(399,261,569,725,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">d) ser titular de mais de um cargo ou mandato p&uacute;blico eletivo.</span></p>'),(400,278,NULL,754,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">a) ordenar apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o do r&eacute;u preso, que permanecer&aacute; sob sua cust&oacute;dia at&eacute; o pronunciamento da Casa sobre o relaxamento ou n&atilde;o da pris&atilde;o;</span></p>'),(401,278,NULL,754,'<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">b) oferecer parecer pr&eacute;vio, facultada a palavra ao Deputado envolvido ou ao seu representante, no prazo de setenta e duas horas, sobre a manuten&ccedil;&atilde;o ou n&atilde;o da pris&atilde;o, propondo o projeto de resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o respectivo, que ser&aacute; submetido at&eacute; a sess&atilde;o seguinte &agrave; delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o do Plen&aacute;rio, pelo voto secreto da maioria de seus membros;</span></p>');
